The players hide near the farm at night.

The wind blows softly through the cornfields.

Suddenly:

CRUNCH.
SQUEAK.
RUSTLE.

Something moves near the pumpkin patch.

Farmer Brindle whispers:

> "There! Did you hear that?"

The players must decide what to do.

