# Phase 2 — Following the Tracks

The players follow clues into the woods.

They discover:
- chewed vegetables
- muddy pawprints
- tunnel entrances hidden beneath tree roots

Eventually, they find a large underground burrow beneath an old windmill.

Inside are:
- piles of vegetables
- tiny cooking fires
- baby rats hiding nervously

The players finally meet:

## Captain Squeaks
Leader of the Burrowband rats.

He explains:
- their tunnels flooded
- their food was destroyed
- they were trying to feed their families

Suddenly, the burrow begins shaking.

Water starts leaking through the tunnel walls.

The underground tunnels are collapsing.

The players must act quickly.

