# Final Ending

## Peaceful Ending
The villagers help rebuild the Burrowband tunnels safely away from the farm.

The rats help protect the crops from pests in return.

Captain Squeaks becomes the official chef of the Harvest Festival soup stand.

The players receive:
- Harvest Hero badges
- golden carrot medals
- unlimited pumpkin pie during the festival

Farmer Brindle says:

> "Sometimes solving problems means listening first."

---

## Funny Chaos Ending
The village becomes completely covered in runaway vegetables and muddy water.

Children laugh while chasing bouncing pumpkins through the streets.

Captain Squeaks accidentally invents pumpkin soup during the chaos.

The Harvest Festival becomes the most memorable celebration Pumpkin Hollow has ever seen.

The players still become local heroes.

---

## Heroic Ending
The players save both the village harvest and the underground rat families.

The villagers no longer fear the Burrowband.

Every year afterward, humans and rats celebrate the Harvest Festival together beneath glowing lanterns around Moonpatch Farm.